Diamond's baby mama Zari Hassan has blasted rapper Japesa for lying about her sliding in his Instagram DMs. Japesa had shared a screenshot claiming the Ugandan Socialite was pursuing him. He shared messages they were allegedly flirting with each other. He then urged his fans not to fear sliding into top celebrities' inboxes. A few hours later, it turned out he was releasing a song titled 'Fine Madam'. Zari took the screenshot of the messages and shared on her Insta stories, asking the singer to stop using her to chase clout. "I never dmd you .. please release your song in peace without chasing clout. I hate when people use my name like this."